divs: Sighting DetailsTook a pic of a jet and contrail, and the two spheres showed up on the jet that were not visible with binoculars. Also if you zoom in there is another something a little higher and to the right of the jet. Oakland County Michigan has been having busy skies
Summary: Spheres and a shape showed up in picture.
